# User Stories

## Employee User Stories  
- As a new employee, I want a mentor during onboarding so I feel supported.  
- As an employee, I want clear information on career paths so I can plan my growth.  
- As an employee, I want regular feedback opportunities to voice concerns and suggestions.

## HR Manager User Stories  
- As HR, I want detailed attrition data to identify turnover patterns.  
- As HR, I want to communicate retention strategies transparently to build trust.

## Acceptance Criteria  
- Mentorship assigned within first week of hire.  
- Career paths clearly documented and communicated company-wide.  
- Employee surveys conducted quarterly with actionable results.
